		{ heading: 'God revealed as Father, not a distant deity', bodyHtml: `In a culture rich with names and images for the divine, the Father&rsquo;s Heart Bible&trade; offers something no English Bible has before: it reveals God as <em>Father</em> wherever Scripture reveals Him that way &mdash; from <a href=\"https://fathersheartbible.com/read/genesis/1\" style=\"color: var(--color-brand);\" class=\"hover:underline\">Genesis 1:1</a> onward. Not a remote power to appease, but a Father who loves His sons and daughters.` },
		{ heading: 'Free, with audio, on any phone', bodyHtml: `No purchase, no app, no sign-up. The whole Bible is free to <a href=\"https://fathersheartbible.com/read\" style=\"color: var(--color-brand);\" class=\"hover:underline\">read online</a> with audio on every chapter &mdash; built to work on a basic smartphone, which is how most of India reads the internet.` },
		{ heading: 'A starting point for every reader', bodyHtml: `New to the Bible? Our <a href=\"/guides/where-to-start-reading-the-bible/\" style=\"color: var(--color-brand);\" class=\"hover:underline\">where-to-start guide</a> and <a href=\"/guides/how-to-read-the-bible/\" style=\"color: var(--color-brand);\" class=\"hover:underline\">how-to-read-the-Bible guide</a> walk you through the first steps, so you&rsquo;re never lost on page one.` },
	]}
